snippet.title: Landinar: Into the Void - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
In this top-down space-adventure-RPG you are recruited as a rookie bounty hunter in the oppressive Landinar Empire. Meet diverse characters, build your own space ship, and fight for the good of humanity.

Buy it now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/794270/Landinar_Into_the_Void/

Join the Discord: https://discord.gg/landinar
